one_reviews_text: This is a nice setup for a 180 3D stereoscopic cinematic experience for VR. Unfortunately, who knows if the rest of the story will ever be told. I liked the film parts of this experience. They were well-acted and the story has a great setup. I did not like the gameplay elements. You basically click when you hear a sound to inspect an object. It's pretty bad. Whole thing took me about 26 minutes.
